{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ba8f4191-2493-5abf-b895-77ce8278e943","html":"<h4 id=\"hey-thanks-for-visiting-im-matt\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hey-thanks-for-visiting-im-matt\" aria-label=\"hey thanks for visiting im matt permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hey, thanks for visiting! I’m Matt.</h4>\n<p>I’m currently studying Mechatronics Engineering with a Software Engineering Minor at the University of Waterloo.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stockholm_syndrome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">I love TypeScript</a> along with some of its frameworks: <em>React</em>, <em>Node</em>, and <em>Express</em>.</p>\n<h4 id=\"where-ive-worked-in-the-past\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#where-ive-worked-in-the-past\" aria-label=\"where ive worked in the past permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Where I’ve worked in the past</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>